  "answer": "```yaml\ninstitution_found_online: true\ninstitution_website: \"https://mammoth.bio/\"\ninstitution_address_on_record: \"1000 Marina Blvd, Brisbane, CA 94005\"\naddress_matches_claimed: false\naddress_match_level: \"none\"\nother_entity_at_address: \"Letterman Digital Arts Center (Lucasfilm, venture capital firms, Parker Institute for Cancer Immunotherapy)\"\ncoworking_or_incubator: false\ncoworking_operator: null\ninstitution_has_multiple_campuses: false\ninstitution_moved_recently: true\nmoved_from: \"Shared incubator in the Dogpatch neighborhood, San Francisco, CA\"\nmoved_to: \"1000 Marina Blvd, Brisbane, CA 94005\"\n\nconfidence: high\nfree_text_summary: |\n  Mammoth Biosciences is a well-known, legitimate biotechnology company co-founded by Jennifer Doudna, but it is not located at the claimed shipping address. The company's official headquarters is at 1000 Marina Blvd in Brisbane, CA. The company previously operated out of a shared incubator in the Dogpatch neighborhood of San Francisco but moved to its current Brisbane facility in July 2019. There is no web evidence connecting Mammoth Biosciences to 1 Letterman Drive. The claimed address (1 Letterman Drive) corresponds to the Letterman Digital Arts Center in the Presidio of San Francisco, a corporate campus that houses Lucasfilm and various venture capital firms, not a specialized biotech incubator or Mammoth's operational labs. \n\nsources:\n  - url: \"https://mammoth.bio/contact/\"\n    domain: \"mammoth.bio\"\n    source_type: \"official_institution_page\"\n    snippet: \"Mammoth Biosciences, Inc. 1000 Marina Blvd. Brisbane, CA 94005\"\n  - url: \"https://mammoth.bio/2019/08/08/moving-to-a-bigger-better-space-mammoth-2-0/\"\n    domain: \"mammoth.bio\"\n    source_type: \"official_institution_page\"\n    snippet: \"For the last year or so we were working out of a shared incubator space in the 'Dog patch' neighborhood of San Francisco... We just completed our move to a huge (dare we say mammoth-size) new space in South San Francisco \u2013 Mammoth 2.0.\"\n  - url: \"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Letterman_Digital_Arts_Center\"\n    domain: \"wikipedia.org\"\n    source_type: \"encyclopedia\"\n    snippet: \"The Letterman Digital Arts Center (LDAC) is a special place in the Presidio area of San Francisco... Since 2005, it has been the main home for several parts of Lucasfilm.\"\n  - url: \"https://www.bizprofile.net/principal-address/1-letterman-drive-suite-c3500-san-francisco-ca-94129\"\n    domain: \"bizprofile.net\"\n    source_type: \"business_directory\"\n    snippet: \"Entities registered at 1 Letterman Drive, Suite C3500 San Francisco, CA 94129... Atomic Labs Partners Iv, L.p.\"\n  - url: \"https://property.jll.com/listings/bldg-d-one-letterman-dr-san-francisco\"\n    domain: \"property.jll.com\"\n    source_type: \"real_estate_listing\"\n    snippet: \"Bldg D One Letterman Dr San Francisco, CA, 94129 ... Space Available for lease 6,256 SF\"\n\nsearches_performed:\n  - query: \"\\\"Mammoth Biosciences\\\" address \\\"San Francisco\\\"\"\n    num_results: 10\n  - query: \"\\\"Mammoth Biosciences\\\" \\\"1 Letterman Drive\\\"\"\n    num_results: 10\n  - query: \"\\\"1 Letterman Drive, Suite D4700\\\"\"\n    num_results: 10\n  - query: \"\\\"Mammoth Biosciences\\\" \\\"Brisbane\\\" \\\"San Francisco\\\" move\"\n    num_results: 10\n  - query: \"\\\"1 Letterman Drive\\\" \\\"D4700\\\" incubator OR coworking OR sublease OR address\"\n    num_results: 10\n  - query: \"\\\"Mammoth Biosciences\\\" \\\"1 Letterman\\\" OR D4700 OR C3500\"\n    num_results: 10\n```",
